The city of eThekweni has once again rolled out the red carpet, or shall we say the black carpet, for the 16th annual Metro FM Music Awards at the Durban ICC tomorrow night.Yesterday, it was revealed that the glitzy awards ceremony will be hosted by the Greatest Escape duo, Pearl Modiadie and Amon Mokoena.The ceremony has become a must attend annual gathering on the social calendar and draws locals from other provinces to the city with a host of pre-parties at various KwaZuluNatal venues ahead of the awards.SIYABONGA SITHOLE|siyabongas@thenewage.co.za